le &acirc;m thanh: AAC (16 to 320 Kbps), Protected AAC (from iTunes Store), MP3 (16 to 320 Kbps), MP3 VBR, Audible (formats 2, 3, and 4), Apple Lossless, WAV, and AIFF</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Định dạng ảnh: JPEG, BMP, GIF, TIFF, PSD (Mac), v&agrave; PNG&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Thời gian sạc: 4h (2h sạc khoảng 80%)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Lưu trữ dữ liệu giống như USB</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Hệ điều h&agrave;nh: Mac OS X, Windows 2000/XP/Vista/Seven...</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ M&agrave;u sắc: Đen</span></p>
