<p><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin chi tiết:</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Dung lượng bộ nhớ: 16GB&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Thời gian sử dụng li&ecirc;n tục: 10h nghe nhạc, 10h xem phim</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh: 9.7" LED đa cảm ứng, độ ph&acirc;n giải 1024 x 760 px</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Chuẩn kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y: Wi-Fi (802.11b/g)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ K&iacute;ch thước: 241.8 x 189.7 x 12.7 mm</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Trọng lượng: 680 g</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Lưu trữ: 4.000 b&agrave;i h&aacute;t (128-Kbps AAC/MP3), 20.000 tấm h&igrave;nh v&agrave; 20h xem Video</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Bluetooth 2.1 + DER</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Ứng dụng: Calendar, Notes, Maps, Contacs, Mail (MobileMe, Yahoo!Mail, Gmail, Hotmail v&agrave; AOL)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ App Store : gần 140.000 ứng dụng d&agrave;nh cho iPad</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ iBooks: 1 c&aacute;ch tuyệt vời để đọc v&agrave; mua s&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n iBookstore</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Pin: Rechargeable lithium polymer battery (Pin sạc).</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Định dạng xem phim: H.264, .m4v, .mp4, v&agrave; .mov</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Định dạng file &acirc;m thanh: AAC (16 to 320 Kbps), Protected AAC (from iTunes Store), MP3 (16 to 320 Kbps), MP3 VBR, Audible (formats 2, 3, and 4), Apple Lossless, WAV, and AIFF</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Định dạng ảnh: JPEG, BMP, GIF, TIFF, PSD (Mac), v&agrave; PNG&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Thời gian sạc: 4h (2h sạc khoảng 80%)</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Lưu trữ dữ liệu giống như USB</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Hệ điều h&agrave;nh: Mac OS X, Windows 2000/XP/Vista/Seven...</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ M&agrave;u sắc: Đen</span></p>
