<p><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ iPad</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Dock Connector to USB Cable</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ 10W USB Power Adapter</span><br /><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">+ Documentation&nbsp;</span></p>";s:8:"warranty";s:1397:"<p>&nbsp;</p>
